Package dnimp

Class Summary
AdvancedTriplet A modifiable convenience data structure holding two integers and one floating point variable.
CMCRender A member of the DNIMP package which handles relevant operations performed on a set of data.
Grid A representation of a grid with a specified dimension capable of containing a collection of points
Pair  
Point A modifiable representation of a DensityNorth Point object containing geospatial information and any one-dimensional set of correlated data.
Statistics A statistics module for the MetCor implementation of different trajectory statistics models.
Triplet A modifiable convenience data structure holding two integers and one floating point variable.
World A representation of all or part of the Northern Hemisphere, segmented into grids with a specified dimension.
